text: Wang Laichun (, born 1966/1967) is a Chinese billionaire, chairwoman and part owner of the electronics manufacturer Luxshare Precision Industry, in Shenzhen, China, which supplies parts to Apple. In 2014, The Daily Telegraph announced that, at the age of 46, she was one of the world's youngest self- made women billionaires. Wang previously worked for ten years for Hon Hai Precision Industry. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Chinese billionaires Category:Chinese business executives Category:Chinese women business executives Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Female billionaires Category:Chinese technology company founders Category:1960s births
